items.name: WP-PostPassManager
items.description: The post-pass plugins on Wordpress are either too expensive or slowing down the system. This Python script provides a straightforward way to manage password protection for posts on a WordPress site. It offers functionalities to both check the current passwords of protected posts and update the password for posts using a specific old password.
